11:["$","p","12",{"className":"mb-6 text-justify leading-8","children":"Hiring a ISO Auditor in UAE- The ISO Auditor in UAE will conduct ISO auditing and the cost will depend on how large and how intricate your organization is. Wizms, ISO consultant in UAE will charge depending on how much time they spend auditing your organization by days. There will be travel costs if the ISO Auditor is not local and there are administrative and accreditation fees as well. Find an ISO Auditor using our free service that allows you to receive three quotes from on top registrars all at once."}]
12:["$","p","13",{"className":"mb-6 text-justify leading-8","children":"Internal Cost- Provide ISO training to the employees to implement the ISO 45001 standard successfully. Our ISO consultant can help you estimate the time needed from employees throughout the project."}]
13:["$","p","14",{"className":"mb-6 text-justify leading-8","children":"Remember to add the cost of the ISO Audit to your total cost estimate. If you are not ready for ISO registration, you may want to explore some of the specific elements of the ISO 45001 certification process such as ISO training, or learning about what an OH&S Risk Analysis is."}]
